Package ch.iserver.ace.algorithm.text

Class Summary
DeleteOperation The DeleteOperation is used to hold a text together with its position that is to be deleted in the document model.
GOTOInclusionTransformation Implementation of the GOTO operational transformation functions.
InsertOperation The InsertOperation is used to hold a text together with its position index.
NoOperation The NoOperation is used to hold a empty text together with the position zero.
SplitOperation The SplitOperation contains two operations.
